extracted_metadata.title: Green Olive + Palestine Children Relief Fund online information session
extracted_metadata.description: A public information and Q&A session on Zoom on 2 March 2021 to discuss the work of PCRF (to which Green Olive donates) and current events in Palestine (including COVID vaccination roll out, the upcoming elections and the Hamas-Fatah split)
